## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources, which may not cover all aspects of the issue comprehensively. The lack of recent data and peer-reviewed academic articles in the search results may limit the depth of the analysis. Additionally, the perspectives provided are primarily from secondary sources, which may not fully capture the complexity of migrant integration challenges in different geopolitical contexts.